title: GoodRx CEO on TrumpRx and Surescripts Partnership
description: GoodRx CEO Wendy Barnes speaks with Katie Greifeld at the JPMorgan Health-Care Conference in San Francisco about TrumpRx and the company's partnership with Surescripts. (Source: Bloomberg)
